title: Black Eagle Rising [Elita Book 3] - Kate Jacoby
description: The sorcerer Nash, grievously wounded by Robert Douglas when he wielded the Word of Destruction, destroyed the evil Malachi and razed Elita to the ground, has spent years rebuilding his strength and increasing the unholy Bond that binds the usurper King Selar to him. But times are changing: Selar plans to spread his iron rule even further, and Robert can no longer ignore the dual threat of Nash and Selar.
